<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.7.9">
<l>veḷḷiyār piṇṭiyār pōtiyā reṉṟiva rōtu kiṉṟa</l>
<l>kaḷḷanūl taṉṉaiyum karumamaṉ ṟeṉṟuyyak karuti ṉāyēl,</l>
<l>teḷḷiyār kaitoḻun tēvaṉār māmunī ramutu tanta</l>
<l>vaḷḷalār vallavāḻ collumā vallaiyāy maruvu neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you intend to be saved, saying that the false texts</l>
<l rend="indent">that those of the silver [mountain],</l>
<l>Those of the aśoka [tree], and those of the peeple [tree] are chanting,</l>
<l rend="indent">are not right,</l>
<l>Oh, heart, firmly embrace the way that tells of Vallavāḻ,</l>
<l rend="indent">[the city of] the liberal one</l>
<l>Who bestowed nectar from the great three-watered [sea],</l>
<l rend="indent">the god whom the wise worship, hands [joined].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
